label: Palisadian-Post
title: Palisadian-Post
exrest: The Palisadian-Post is a bi-weekly subscription newspaper serving Pacific Palisades, California, published every other Thursday by the Pacific Palisades Post. The company also publishes 90272 Magazine and the weekly newspaper The Shopper, also known as the Post-Shopper. The Palisadian Post was founded in 1928 and is currently owned by Palisadian Alan Smolinisky, who was born and raised in Pacific Palisades. The newspaper's editor-in-chief is Sarah Shmerling.
